Did a small bit of skirting board painting in the bathroom! It's a tiny room so took no time at all. I have to admit, it may not have been such a great idea insisting on finishing 90% of this last night. I am so tired and I am crankier than Zayden gets at times. 😅 
So I'm glad he's actually feeling better today. He's back to his normal active, happy toddler self. 😂 I hate seeing my babies sick. Especially when it seemed like it just came from out of nowhere. 
Anyway, this is a poster for Zenon's 5K tomorrow. He joined his school's running club again for spring. So this will be the 2nd 5K he runs by himself. 
Hopefully he runs the whole thing this time...which he probably will because this time we decided that his dad will be running, too. His dad was a runner and he sees the innate talent in Zenon and really wants to show Zenon that he can do it as long as he believes he can. Unfortunately, Zenon got that negativity from me. 
This is also why this time, I made a poster especially for him. It's going to be a surprise. I hope he likes it and really motivates him! 😊❤️❤️❤️🙏🙏🙏 #Zenon #running #5K #starwars #yoda #motivation #posters #oracal #oracal631 #oracal651 #vinyl #cardstock #silhouettecameo #artsandcrafts #runninglife #schoolrunningclub
